      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to hit the road! It\u2019s an honest, hard-working car that shows some signs of its journey, but it remains a solid choice for anyone needing reliable transportation at a great value. Perfect for a daily commuter who appreciates a car with character and plenty of miles still to go!",
