      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It shows visible wear and tear on the interior and exterior, and some mechanical components may require maintenance soon. The car is functional but shows its age.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
