    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and a rough-idling engine that requires immediate attention. The exterior has extensive body damage, including rust spots and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts car, as it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
